WEBVTT

01:42.320 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:51.840 --> 01:53.440
But I can't resist temptation.

01:54.800 --> 01:56.040
What kind of temptation?

01:57.280 --> 01:59.760
If someone is dating in front of me,

01:59.840 --> 02:01.320
I'll also want to date.

02:02.520 --> 02:04.760
Who is dating?
You watch too many idol dramas.

02:04.840 --> 02:05.760
The people close to me.

02:06.560 --> 02:07.960
Those around me.

02:08.919 --> 02:10.240
Are you talking about me?

02:13.040 --> 02:13.920
Kiddo.

02:14.400 --> 02:16.560
Why are you so petty?

02:16.640 --> 02:19.000
You can't stop others from dating
just because you can't date.

02:19.600 --> 02:21.160
Isn't it a provocation

02:21.240 --> 02:22.280
to date in front of me?

02:24.040 --> 02:26.320
Fine, let's say you're right.

02:26.880 --> 02:28.840
I won't talk about the future for now.

02:29.760 --> 02:31.120
But we're going to talk

02:31.720 --> 02:33.240
about your old boyfriend

02:33.320 --> 02:35.720
who told you to go to Yihe to meet him.

02:36.880 --> 02:37.920
It's quite a coincidence

02:38.440 --> 02:40.160
because I'm from Yihe.

02:40.840 --> 02:43.600
So if I ever find out

02:43.680 --> 02:46.120
that you went to see him
while you're still a minor,

02:49.400 --> 02:50.360
then I'm afraid

02:51.240 --> 02:54.120
you won't live to become an adult.

03:01.120 --> 03:02.040
Let's begin the lesson.

03:25.960 --> 03:27.040
How was the last exam?

03:27.520 --> 03:29.600
Take point M
as the intersection on side AB.

03:29.680 --> 03:31.520
I explained it before. Like this problem.

03:31.600 --> 03:33.360
Then try to recall the formula.

03:36.320 --> 03:37.960
I'll explain static electricity first.

03:39.800 --> 03:40.960
You got this problem correct.

03:58.480 --> 03:59.360
This problem.

03:59.440 --> 04:01.120
I was originally going to choose C.

04:02.400 --> 04:03.320
C, you say?

04:04.120 --> 04:05.160
I meant D.

04:08.240 --> 04:09.480
D is the answer to this problem.

04:09.960 --> 04:11.280
Pay more attention next time.

04:20.120 --> 04:21.959
One incorrect multiple-choice problem.

04:23.240 --> 04:24.280
You got 97 points.

04:26.000 --> 04:27.200
Not bad.

04:27.280 --> 04:28.280
You've improved a lot.

04:29.080 --> 04:30.120
So,

04:31.360 --> 04:32.880
you have no problem with physics now.

04:32.960 --> 04:35.040
I won't come to tutor you anymore.

04:35.600 --> 04:37.480
If there is anything you don't understand,

04:37.560 --> 04:38.640
you can ask your brother

04:38.720 --> 04:39.640
or your teacher.

04:39.720 --> 04:40.560
You can ask me too.

04:41.360 --> 04:43.360
Just send me a picture
of what you don't understand.

04:43.440 --> 04:44.840
I'll reply after I go through it.

04:44.920 --> 04:46.080
My phone was confiscated.

04:48.360 --> 04:50.520
Your brother will talk to your parents.

04:55.560 --> 04:56.480
Don't worry.

04:59.040 --> 05:00.000
Cheer up.

05:01.360 --> 05:02.800
You've improved so much now.

05:04.440 --> 05:05.720
So did I teach well?

05:11.040 --> 05:11.920
All right then.

05:12.000 --> 05:14.440
So will you have more exams
after school starts?

05:15.040 --> 05:15.920
Yes.

05:16.000 --> 05:19.480
Then send me each exam's result.

05:20.040 --> 05:21.480
You had better get high scores.

05:22.360 --> 05:24.040
As long as there's an improvement,

05:24.120 --> 05:25.520
I'll give you a gift.

05:31.880 --> 05:32.920
Let's stop here for today.

05:48.680 --> 05:52.480
HAPPY LUNAR NEW YEAR

05:58.360 --> 05:59.480
Are you doing housework?

05:59.560 --> 06:00.720
Is the lesson over?

06:00.800 --> 06:02.360
- Yes.
- Come and have some fruit.

06:03.600 --> 06:05.120
- Thank you, Mrs. Sang.
- Have some fruit.

06:07.600 --> 06:09.400
I was just talking to my husband.

06:09.480 --> 06:11.280
Let's celebrate
Lunar New Year's Eve together.

06:11.360 --> 06:12.240
Come and join us.

06:12.320 --> 06:13.520
Thank you for inviting me.

06:13.600 --> 06:16.360
But I think I'll stay on campus.

06:16.440 --> 06:17.960
It's amazing at school now.

06:18.040 --> 06:19.160
They host a holiday dinner

06:19.240 --> 06:20.280
and give us red packets.

06:21.240 --> 06:22.480
Don't go back.

06:22.560 --> 06:24.000
It will be boring being alone.

06:24.520 --> 06:25.640
In that case,

06:25.720 --> 06:26.680
all right then.

06:27.720 --> 06:28.760
Let me help you, Mr. Sang.

06:28.840 --> 06:30.200
Okay. Sang Zhi, pass that to me.

06:31.240 --> 06:32.200
This one.

06:34.240 --> 06:35.160
Let's stick it here.

06:35.760 --> 06:37.640
This one needs to be upside down.

06:37.720 --> 06:39.160
Is this one good, dear?

06:39.240 --> 06:40.280
Should it be bigger?

06:54.600 --> 06:56.000
If I give him a red packet,

06:56.480 --> 06:57.920
it will seem a bit strange.

06:58.800 --> 07:00.240
He definitely won't accept it.

07:27.160 --> 07:28.000
Jiaxu,

07:28.760 --> 07:29.920
Happy Lunar New Year.

07:54.320 --> 07:55.560
PROSPERITY

08:06.080 --> 08:07.240
Sang Yan said

08:07.720 --> 08:09.280
you'll stay in Nanwu after graduation.

08:09.360 --> 08:10.400
Have you found a job?

08:11.240 --> 08:14.160
Yes, I plan to work at the game company

08:14.240 --> 08:15.360
where I interned.

08:16.000 --> 08:17.000
That's great.

08:18.480 --> 08:19.520
Keep it up.

08:19.600 --> 08:20.560
Okay, let's put it up.

08:21.120 --> 08:22.160
Allow me.

08:23.080 --> 08:24.320
Having it up there will be good.

08:24.400 --> 08:25.600
At the top.

08:25.680 --> 08:26.720
- A bit higher.
- Higher.

08:27.360 --> 08:29.080
- Zhizhi.
- Perfect. All right.

08:29.160 --> 08:30.600
Help me clear the table.

08:30.680 --> 08:31.600
Right here.

08:33.200 --> 08:34.320
Stop sweeping already.

08:34.400 --> 08:36.159
Wash the rag and wipe the table.

08:36.240 --> 08:37.120
Okay.

08:42.720 --> 08:44.600
- It's all done.
- Okay, thank you.

08:45.320 --> 08:46.200
Of course.

08:58.760 --> 09:00.200
GOOD FORTUNE

09:36.000 --> 09:40.560
GOOD FORTUNE

09:40.640 --> 09:41.560
How does it look?

09:54.400 --> 09:55.400
Okay.

09:55.480 --> 09:57.560
- That's enough.
- So little?

09:57.640 --> 09:58.920
That's enough for me. Thank you.

09:59.000 --> 10:01.160
Okay. It's time to toast.

10:01.240 --> 10:02.400
Happy Lunar New Year!

10:02.480 --> 10:05.680
- Happy Lunar New Year!
- Happy Lunar New Year!

10:05.760 --> 10:07.240
- Dear, Happy Lunar New Year.
- Cheers.

10:07.320 --> 10:09.000
I dare you to finish all of this.

10:09.080 --> 10:10.920
- Cheers.
- Go away!

10:11.000 --> 10:12.880
- He won't clink glasses.
- It's such a big bottle.

10:17.000 --> 10:18.120
The most exciting part

10:18.200 --> 10:19.840
is yet to come.

10:21.720 --> 10:23.400
Dear, you'll be the first to get this.

10:23.920 --> 10:24.960
Do I get a red packet too?

10:26.120 --> 10:27.080
Perfect.

10:27.640 --> 10:28.640
Thank you, dear.

10:28.720 --> 10:29.960
I love you.

10:32.720 --> 10:36.360
- Dad and Mom, Happy New Year!
- Dad and Mom, Happy New Year!

10:36.440 --> 10:37.760
- May your wishes come true!
- May your wishes come true!

10:37.840 --> 10:39.080
- Be happy…
- Stay healthy…

10:39.160 --> 10:40.520
"Be happy" comes first.

10:40.600 --> 10:41.440
It's "stay healthy".

10:41.520 --> 10:43.560
No, it's "be happy"!

10:43.640 --> 10:44.840
Fine.

10:44.920 --> 10:46.600
- Be happy every day!
- Be happy every day!

10:46.680 --> 10:48.960
- Stay healthy!
- Stay healthy!

10:49.040 --> 10:50.640
- I like it.
- Good. Here you go, Sang Yan.

10:50.720 --> 10:52.000
Thank you, Dad.

10:52.080 --> 10:53.480
Sang Zhi, this is yours.

10:55.640 --> 10:56.560
Thank you, Dad.

10:56.640 --> 10:58.040
- Dad.
- Thank you, Mom.

10:58.120 --> 10:59.800
You're being so unfair.

11:00.360 --> 11:01.760
You're almost a university graduate.

11:01.840 --> 11:03.160
You're lucky to even receive one.

11:03.680 --> 11:04.600
Sang Zhi.

11:05.520 --> 11:07.560
What should you do
after getting your phone?

11:08.880 --> 11:10.480
I'll uninstall the games.

11:10.560 --> 11:11.400
What else?

11:11.880 --> 11:13.760
What about your online dating prospect?

11:18.480 --> 11:19.840
I already deleted it long ago.

11:21.400 --> 11:22.640
What about his phone number?

11:23.480 --> 11:24.560
I don't have his number.

11:24.640 --> 11:26.200
Online dating doesn't use phone numbers.

11:26.280 --> 11:27.440
I'm telling the truth.

11:29.400 --> 11:30.280
Really?

11:31.800 --> 11:33.080
You can see for yourself.

11:34.640 --> 11:36.760
You don't even have enough money

11:36.840 --> 11:38.400
to afford game currency.

11:38.480 --> 11:40.600
- Why are you dating online?
- Stop talking already.

11:40.680 --> 11:42.760
- All right.
- Cut it out. Stop arguing.

11:43.680 --> 11:44.680
- Let's eat.
- Eat up.

11:44.760 --> 11:46.560
I have something to say before we eat.

11:46.640 --> 11:47.560
I hope

11:48.280 --> 11:50.880
my two lovely children will grow up

11:50.960 --> 11:53.320
and behave a bit more

11:53.400 --> 11:55.120
in this new year.

11:55.200 --> 11:56.480
And you.

11:56.560 --> 11:57.840
- Be more mature.
- He means you.

12:00.320 --> 12:02.360
- All right, let's eat.
- Okay, let's dig in.

12:04.880 --> 12:06.320
By the way, Zhizhi.

12:06.400 --> 12:08.200
Didn't you want

12:08.280 --> 12:09.760
to buy a set of anime merchandise?

12:10.240 --> 12:11.960
Now that your brother has money,

12:12.040 --> 12:13.280
ask him to buy it for you.

12:14.120 --> 12:15.680
Why should I? No way.

12:15.760 --> 12:17.480
Thank you, Sang Yan. Thank you.

12:24.120 --> 12:25.680
Sang Yan is the most generous.

12:26.160 --> 12:27.480
Sang Yan, have some of this.

12:27.560 --> 12:28.600
A toast to Sang Yan.

12:28.680 --> 12:30.360
- Happy New Year.
- Happy New Year.

12:32.160 --> 12:33.000
This is for you.

12:34.840 --> 12:36.480
At least you have a conscience.

12:36.560 --> 12:38.440
- But it's not much.
- You like eating this.

12:41.160 --> 12:42.600
- It's delicious.
- Really?

12:43.760 --> 12:44.880
I want this one.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.760
JIAXU

12:56.720 --> 12:57.640
It's from Jiaxu.

13:01.600 --> 13:03.080
Sang Yan, you did well. Have more.

13:03.160 --> 13:04.640
- Thank you, Mom.
- Should we go on a trip?

13:05.440 --> 13:07.480
Sang Zhi, I wish you happiness every day

13:07.560 --> 13:08.800
and find your dreams soon.

13:08.880 --> 13:09.920
Happy Lunar New Year.

13:10.520 --> 13:11.920
- Sure.
- Zhizhi.

13:12.480 --> 13:14.360
How about going skiing in a few days?

13:15.240 --> 13:17.160
Skiing? Sure.

13:17.240 --> 13:19.440
Okay, then make up an itinerary for us.

13:19.520 --> 13:21.440
- Okay.
- It's busy during the holidays.

13:21.520 --> 13:22.760
- So book early.
- That's right.

13:29.480 --> 13:31.480
- Next to number three.
- Forget about numbers.

13:31.560 --> 13:32.760
How about salt with vinegar?

13:32.840 --> 13:34.680
- Footsteps.
- Listen to my upper couplet.

13:34.760 --> 13:36.040
It starts with "Perfectly."

13:36.120 --> 13:37.560
- Damn.
- "Perfectly matched."

13:37.640 --> 13:38.920
- What matched?
- Behind the bridge.

13:39.000 --> 13:41.400
Perfectly matched, matched as in paired.

13:41.480 --> 13:42.400
That's a good start.

13:42.480 --> 13:43.920
I follow that with Minister.

13:44.000 --> 13:45.440
- Move.
- Minister against Cannon.

13:47.480 --> 13:48.840
Why is it Minister against Cannon?

13:48.920 --> 13:51.440
You move the Minister,
and I counter with the Cannon.

13:52.000 --> 13:53.840
It's Chinese chess. Get it?

13:53.920 --> 13:55.240
I'll put it this way.

13:55.320 --> 13:57.160
I structured
these five characters together.

14:02.640 --> 14:03.720
Thank you, Jiaxu.

14:04.920 --> 14:06.080
Happy Lunar New Year.

14:19.560 --> 14:21.960
YIHE CITY NURSING HOME

14:32.640 --> 14:33.680
ANSWER

14:33.760 --> 14:34.800
YIHE CITY NURSING HOME

14:36.760 --> 14:37.840
Hello?

14:37.920 --> 14:39.840
Hello. Are you Mr. Duan Jiaxu?

14:39.920 --> 14:41.080
Yes.

14:41.640 --> 14:44.320
Your dad has severe pulmonary edema
caused by a lung infection

14:44.400 --> 14:46.280
and must be transferred immediately
for drainage.

14:48.080 --> 14:49.680
The current condition is quite urgent.

14:49.760 --> 14:52.320
Please come as soon as possible
to sign the consent form.

14:53.000 --> 14:54.760
Okay, I understand. Thank you.

15:27.160 --> 15:29.320
CHAPTER SIX, DISTANCE

15:29.400 --> 15:31.320
WHEN YOU ARE IN ANOTHER CITY

15:33.880 --> 15:35.400
Mr. Sang, your package.

15:35.480 --> 15:36.320
Okay, thank you.

15:42.800 --> 15:43.640
Hey, silly dog.

15:46.080 --> 15:47.920
It has a name. It's Winner.

15:49.160 --> 15:50.400
Silly dog, come here.

15:51.120 --> 15:52.240
Come here. Let me tell you.

15:52.320 --> 15:53.320
Come here.

15:53.400 --> 15:55.080
Listen. Look.

15:55.760 --> 15:58.000
You look so similar to him.

15:58.080 --> 15:59.640
You two look exactly alike.

16:09.560 --> 16:10.480
Wait right there.

16:11.720 --> 16:13.000
Duan Jiaxu sent this to you.

16:13.080 --> 16:14.760
It's your reward for ranking 20th

16:14.840 --> 16:16.080
in the placement test

16:16.160 --> 16:17.680
and scoring 95 on the physics exam.

16:19.760 --> 16:22.080
Why didn't he give it to me himself?

16:22.160 --> 16:23.000
Didn't he tell you?

16:23.080 --> 16:24.320
He went back to his hometown.

16:24.800 --> 16:25.920
He's back in Yihe.

16:26.000 --> 16:27.720
He said something came up at home.

16:28.400 --> 16:30.120
Why don't you ask him yourself?

16:34.360 --> 16:35.200
Wait.

16:35.280 --> 16:38.200
Then will he come back
for the graduation ceremony?

16:38.760 --> 16:40.200
Of course he will.

16:43.760 --> 16:46.520
Why did he leave without saying goodbye?

17:05.240 --> 17:08.160
XURI MIDDLE-HIGH SCHOOL
TO NANWU UNIVERSITY

17:10.720 --> 17:13.079
2 HOURS AND 33 MINUTES

17:17.000 --> 17:19.160
Sang Yan, are you coming home today?

17:26.920 --> 17:30.840
SILLY DOG

17:30.920 --> 17:32.280
What does this mean?

17:34.520 --> 17:36.600
Why are you taking your time
when class is over?

17:37.920 --> 17:39.480
My sister is probably in trouble again.

17:39.560 --> 17:41.040
She asked if I'm going home.

17:41.120 --> 17:42.280
Is she in trouble again?

18:02.600 --> 18:03.720
It was awesome just now,

18:03.800 --> 18:05.720
tossing the basketball with this pose.

18:05.800 --> 18:07.840
I was off my game today.

18:13.000 --> 18:13.920
Hello?

18:14.760 --> 18:15.960
Sang Yan, it's already Friday.

18:16.040 --> 18:17.120
Why aren't you coming home?

18:18.000 --> 18:19.560
There's a BOGO promotion on candy

18:19.640 --> 18:20.880
at the convenience store today.

18:20.960 --> 18:23.040
I bought an extra pack.
I can share it with you.

18:23.960 --> 18:25.400
If I want candy, I can buy it myself.

18:25.960 --> 18:27.320
Just tell me what you want.

18:27.880 --> 18:30.200
Nothing. I'm just asking.

18:30.680 --> 18:32.640
Well, I can just not go home.

18:32.720 --> 18:34.040
- Right?
- It was cheap.

18:34.120 --> 18:35.880
- You can invite friends over.
- Duan Jiaxu!

18:38.600 --> 18:39.560
Where are you going?

18:39.640 --> 18:40.680
Where are you guys going?

18:40.760 --> 18:41.760
I'm going home for a bit.

18:42.720 --> 18:44.240
I happen to be going to your area.

18:44.320 --> 18:45.320
Let's go together.

18:45.400 --> 18:47.680
Sure. Come over for dinner if you're free.

18:47.760 --> 18:48.600
Okay.

18:50.040 --> 18:51.040
I'm not joining you.

18:51.120 --> 18:52.400
I'm going back to the dorm.

18:52.480 --> 18:53.480
- Okay.
- Bye.

18:53.560 --> 18:54.520
Bye.

18:54.600 --> 18:56.560
- Hello, little demon.
- Suspicious.

18:57.360 --> 18:58.240
What's wrong?

18:58.760 --> 18:59.600
She hung up on me.

18:59.680 --> 19:00.560
Let's go.

19:23.840 --> 19:25.360
Why don't I call Sang Yan

19:25.440 --> 19:27.000
and ask where they are?

19:34.480 --> 19:35.320
Forget it.

19:35.880 --> 19:37.280
They should be here soon.

19:40.600 --> 19:42.480
Don't worry. What's the situation?

19:47.120 --> 19:49.040
- Again, Chen Junwen?
- He's finally home!

19:49.880 --> 19:51.960
How many times
have you forgotten your keys?

19:53.680 --> 19:54.840
I can't bring it to you.

19:54.920 --> 19:56.080
You come to get it yourself.

19:58.520 --> 20:00.400
Did you forget to bring your brain too?

20:00.480 --> 20:02.280
I'm already home.
How can I open it for you?

20:03.000 --> 20:05.000
Why is he alone?

20:07.560 --> 20:08.400
Little demon!

20:09.320 --> 20:10.880
Why didn't you close the door?

20:10.960 --> 20:12.000
There are mosquitoes!

20:12.840 --> 20:14.720
Duan Jiaxu was supposed to come with me,

20:14.800 --> 20:16.280
but the library gave him a call,

20:16.360 --> 20:17.520
so he had to go back to work.

20:17.600 --> 20:19.720
As you know,
he's crazy about making money.

20:21.040 --> 20:22.440
All right, that's all.

20:22.520 --> 20:23.400
I'm hanging up now.

20:24.320 --> 20:25.360
Bye.

20:26.200 --> 20:27.160
Little demon.

20:28.640 --> 20:29.920
Why did you want me home?

20:32.440 --> 20:33.400
Dad and Mom wanted

20:33.480 --> 20:35.080
to have dinner together this weekend.

20:35.160 --> 20:37.000
Have dinner together?

20:38.960 --> 20:40.880
Couldn't you tell me over the phone?

20:42.720 --> 20:44.160
Dad! Mom!

20:44.240 --> 20:45.760
Sang Yan? Sang Yan is back.

20:45.840 --> 20:48.320
I thought you were coming home tomorrow.

20:52.440 --> 20:54.320
Let's have dinner together this weekend.

20:55.840 --> 20:57.040
You're getting more thoughtful.

20:58.240 --> 21:00.000
We're sweaty from a day of work.

21:00.080 --> 21:00.920
We'll shower first.

21:01.000 --> 21:01.840
- Okay.
- Okay.

21:01.920 --> 21:03.040
Afterward, I'll make dinner.

21:03.120 --> 21:04.240
Okay.

21:04.320 --> 21:06.720
Mom, why not let Sang Yan make dinner?

21:06.800 --> 21:08.120
Let him make dinner?

21:08.200 --> 21:09.280
That would work too.

21:09.360 --> 21:10.560
Cook the rice first.

21:10.640 --> 21:11.800
Wash the vegetables too.

21:11.880 --> 21:13.480
Cooking rice is too simple.

21:13.560 --> 21:15.320
It's okay. Let him cook the rice.

21:15.400 --> 21:16.360
I'll cook the rest.

21:29.280 --> 21:30.240
Sang Yan.

21:30.320 --> 21:32.480
Which library is Jiaxu working at?

21:32.560 --> 21:33.960
Is it the university's library?

21:36.560 --> 21:37.680
Why are you asking me this?

21:38.760 --> 21:40.600
Nothing. I'm just curious.

21:40.680 --> 21:42.360
Are all university students so busy?

21:43.280 --> 21:44.920
What are you usually busy with?

21:45.000 --> 21:47.600
I'm busy trying to get away
from a little demon like you.

21:48.400 --> 21:49.520
Busy sleeping in class.

21:51.120 --> 21:52.920
Isn't that the same
as middle school students?

21:54.240 --> 21:55.920
How can it be the same?

21:56.000 --> 21:58.040
University students
have one more thing to do,

21:58.120 --> 21:59.000
which is dating.

21:59.880 --> 22:00.720
Dating?

22:02.720 --> 22:03.720
Well, I should've known.

22:03.800 --> 22:06.240
A kid like you wouldn't understand this.

22:06.320 --> 22:07.600
How is that possible?

22:07.680 --> 22:09.200
Why would any girl like you?

22:10.360 --> 22:12.640
Listen, plenty of girls chase after me.

22:12.720 --> 22:14.840
Not even a high-speed train
can fit them all.

22:17.640 --> 22:18.520
What's wrong with you?

22:19.160 --> 22:20.520
It has been so long

22:20.600 --> 22:21.920
since I've heard anyone

22:22.000 --> 22:23.880
tell such a tall tale.

22:24.880 --> 22:25.720
You don't believe me?

22:26.560 --> 22:28.080
Okay, listen.

22:29.200 --> 22:30.400
Do you know why

22:30.480 --> 22:33.160
none of my roommates have girlfriends?

22:34.960 --> 22:37.600
None of them have girlfriends?

22:37.680 --> 22:39.360
It's because those girls

22:39.440 --> 22:40.880
are lining up to pursue me.

22:41.840 --> 22:43.160
Who would believe that nonsense?

22:58.280 --> 22:59.680
SENDER, DUAN JIAXU

23:01.760 --> 23:04.200
Another reward from Jiaxu
for my exam scores.

23:59.360 --> 24:00.200
Hello?

24:01.000 --> 24:01.960
Hello, Jiaxu.

24:03.720 --> 24:05.960
I received the package you sent.

24:06.040 --> 24:08.120
It's a black dog plushie.

24:10.400 --> 24:12.200
So? Do you like it?

24:14.280 --> 24:17.840
It looks a bit familiar to me.

24:17.920 --> 24:18.920
Is that so?

24:19.720 --> 24:21.600
Does it look like Sang Yan?

24:26.080 --> 24:27.920
You still remember my essay.

24:28.000 --> 24:29.160
Of course I do.

24:30.240 --> 24:31.920
I was walking on the street one day

24:32.000 --> 24:33.240
and saw this dog.

24:34.240 --> 24:36.240
It reminded me of your drawing back then.

24:37.360 --> 24:38.800
So I thought

24:38.880 --> 24:40.320
it would be a perfect gift for you.

24:40.840 --> 24:42.320
Congratulations on scoring 95 points

24:42.400 --> 24:43.560
on the physics exam this time.

24:46.400 --> 24:47.720
By the way, Jiaxu.

24:47.800 --> 24:49.560
Give me your address.

24:50.280 --> 24:51.680
I want to send you something.

24:52.720 --> 24:54.080
Do you want to send me something?

24:55.160 --> 24:56.640
I'm just exchanging favors.

24:58.600 --> 24:59.560
No need.

25:00.360 --> 25:02.200
Why? It's important.

25:03.320 --> 25:05.160
What is your monthly allowance?

25:05.640 --> 25:07.320
Keep the money

25:07.400 --> 25:08.840
and spend it on yourself, okay?

25:08.920 --> 25:10.160
No need to send me any gifts.

25:10.760 --> 25:11.920
Let me send you something.

25:13.000 --> 25:14.400
You really don't have to.

25:14.480 --> 25:15.640
The fact that you want to

25:15.720 --> 25:17.240
already makes me happy.

25:19.200 --> 25:21.920
So Sang Yan said

25:22.000 --> 25:25.240
you will come back
for your graduation ceremony.

25:25.320 --> 25:26.160
Is that true?

25:26.240 --> 25:27.360
Yes.

25:27.840 --> 25:28.920
Will you be going?

25:30.280 --> 25:31.320
Yes.

25:32.080 --> 25:33.080
That's great.

25:33.160 --> 25:34.480
We'll see each other then.

25:36.880 --> 25:38.000
I have to go now.

25:38.760 --> 25:39.600
Bye.

25:40.160 --> 25:41.040
Bye.

25:56.480 --> 25:58.600
Then consider it your graduation gift.

26:13.720 --> 26:14.680
Who's there?

26:21.480 --> 26:22.560
It has been a long time.

26:25.520 --> 26:26.560
Why are you here?

26:28.320 --> 26:30.080
Aren't you inviting me in?

26:32.480 --> 26:33.560
It's not a good time.

26:34.160 --> 26:35.200
Sorry about that.

26:41.200 --> 26:42.240
Here.

26:43.920 --> 26:46.280
Isn't that person in a bad condition?

26:46.760 --> 26:47.960
Don't worry

26:48.040 --> 26:49.480
about returning the money this month.

26:50.880 --> 26:51.800
It's fine.

26:52.280 --> 26:53.440
I can figure it out myself.

26:54.400 --> 26:56.440
I just don't want you to have a hard time.

26:56.520 --> 26:58.320
It's really not necessary. Thank you.

27:01.920 --> 27:02.760
By the way,

27:02.840 --> 27:05.280
has the time for your graduation ceremony
been set yet?

27:05.360 --> 27:06.880
Can I go too?

27:10.480 --> 27:11.480
No need.

27:18.480 --> 27:19.600
It's all right.

27:19.680 --> 27:21.200
Since you're returning to Yihe,

27:21.280 --> 27:22.920
we'll get a chance to meet up.

27:24.040 --> 27:25.480
Then

27:25.560 --> 27:27.480
I wish you an early happy graduation.

27:27.560 --> 27:28.680
Thank you.

27:30.560 --> 27:31.920
I'll be in touch.

27:59.360 --> 28:01.080
- Three, two, one!
- Three, two, one!

28:01.160 --> 28:02.760
- Cheese!
- Cheese!

28:02.840 --> 28:04.160
Smile a little.

28:04.240 --> 28:05.120
A bit lower.

28:05.680 --> 28:07.160
Okay, smile.

28:07.240 --> 28:09.320
- Three, two, one.
- Hi, Sang Yan.

28:09.400 --> 28:10.520
Your classmate?

28:10.600 --> 28:11.680
Actually, I don't know him.

28:11.760 --> 28:13.120
- Sang Yan!
- Sang Yan, come here!

28:13.200 --> 28:14.120
Over there.

28:23.200 --> 28:24.520
- Hello, Mr. Sang.
- Hello, Mr. Sang.

28:24.600 --> 28:25.760
Congratulations on graduating.

28:26.640 --> 28:28.000
Thank you, Mr. Sang.

28:32.000 --> 28:33.680
Mr. Sang, where is Mrs. Sang?

28:33.760 --> 28:36.560
She's sick with a cold and fever.

28:36.640 --> 28:37.880
I told her to rest at home.

28:37.960 --> 28:40.240
- Many people have fallen sick lately.
- Yes.

28:40.320 --> 28:41.280
Sang Yan, you're late.

28:41.360 --> 28:42.920
We need to take a picture together.

28:43.000 --> 28:44.400
Okay, come on.

28:44.480 --> 28:46.720
- Let me help you take it.
- Thank you, Mr. Sang.

28:46.800 --> 28:47.800
No problem.

28:49.360 --> 28:50.520
Look this way.

28:50.600 --> 28:53.120
One, two, three.

28:53.200 --> 28:54.200
Make a different pose.

28:55.440 --> 28:57.760
Ready? One, two, three.

28:57.840 --> 28:59.080
It's all done. Take a look.

29:00.000 --> 29:01.440
- Thank you, Mr. Sang.
- Qian Fei!

29:02.520 --> 29:04.040
- Take pictures with us!
- Come, Qian Fei!

29:04.120 --> 29:04.960
- Come on!
- Let's go.

29:05.040 --> 29:06.360
- Come!
- Dad, I'm going over there.

29:06.440 --> 29:07.640
Jiaxu, come and join us.

29:07.720 --> 29:08.600
- Come!
- I'm coming!

29:08.680 --> 29:10.720
I heard you'll work in your hometown.

29:11.200 --> 29:13.240
Yes. I've already found a job.

29:14.360 --> 29:15.840
That's not a bad idea either.

29:15.920 --> 29:17.560
After all, you're familiar with the area.

29:18.960 --> 29:20.080
If you ever visit Nanwu,

29:20.160 --> 29:21.360
come to my house for a meal.

29:21.440 --> 29:22.640
Okay, that's for sure.

29:22.720 --> 29:23.680
Good.

29:23.760 --> 29:25.560
Let's go take a photo with your brother.

29:25.640 --> 29:26.880
- Let's take it together.
- Okay.

29:30.360 --> 29:31.760
It has been a long time, Sang Zhi.

29:37.000 --> 29:38.320
This is for you.

29:39.480 --> 29:40.520
For me?

29:42.680 --> 29:44.400
I thought it was for your brother.

29:45.480 --> 29:47.400
He already has one.

29:48.320 --> 29:50.520
This one is for my physics tutor.

29:51.280 --> 29:52.400
I wish you

29:52.480 --> 29:53.680
a happy graduation

29:53.760 --> 29:54.760
and happiness every day.

29:56.040 --> 29:56.880
Thank you.

29:57.760 --> 29:58.600
I like it very much.

30:00.240 --> 30:02.160
Then I wish my student

30:02.240 --> 30:03.400
a bright future

30:03.480 --> 30:04.640
and smooth academic progress.

30:06.840 --> 30:08.880
The graduation ceremony is about to begin.

30:08.960 --> 30:10.080
All graduating students,

30:10.160 --> 30:11.680
please gather in the auditorium.

30:13.560 --> 30:14.920
Jiaxu, you should go ahead.

30:15.000 --> 30:16.960
I'll go and find my brother by myself.

30:17.520 --> 30:18.880
It's okay. I'll take you there.

30:18.960 --> 30:20.120
I'll text your brother.

30:22.200 --> 30:23.240
Come on.

30:34.120 --> 30:35.360
- Jiaxu.
- Jiaxu.

30:35.440 --> 30:36.880
- Hey, Jiaxu.
- Come and join us.

30:36.960 --> 30:38.280
- Come take a picture.
- Okay.

30:38.360 --> 30:39.880
I'll take a picture with them.

30:39.960 --> 30:41.280
Jiaxu, who is this?

30:42.240 --> 30:43.840
My sister.

30:43.920 --> 30:45.920
Hi. Can you help us take a photo?

30:46.520 --> 30:47.360
Sure.

30:47.440 --> 30:49.880
- Thank you. Just press this.
- Okay.

30:49.960 --> 30:50.800
Come on, everyone.

30:50.880 --> 30:51.920
- Come on.
- Picture time.

30:52.000 --> 30:52.880
- Okay.
- This is it.

30:52.960 --> 30:54.280
- Stand there.
- Okay.

30:54.360 --> 30:55.280
Okay.

30:55.360 --> 30:56.360
Three.

30:56.440 --> 30:57.640
Two.

30:57.720 --> 30:58.560
One.

30:59.760 --> 31:00.680
Good.

31:00.760 --> 31:01.680
Okay, thank you.

31:01.760 --> 31:03.440
- Jiaxu.
- It's a great picture.

31:03.520 --> 31:05.680
Professor Zhang, thank you for your help.

31:05.760 --> 31:07.680
I hope to see you shine and excel

31:07.760 --> 31:10.880
in the gaming industry.

31:10.960 --> 31:12.680
- I'll do my best.
- I believe in you.

31:12.760 --> 31:13.640
Thank you.

31:13.720 --> 31:15.560
Okay, I'm going inside first.

31:15.640 --> 31:16.840
- Okay.
- Okay, Professor.

31:17.480 --> 31:18.400
Jiaxu.

31:19.280 --> 31:21.880
Participating in competitions
and research projects with you

31:21.960 --> 31:23.760
was the most painful
and happiest thing for me

31:23.840 --> 31:25.200
in these four years.

31:25.280 --> 31:26.480
Both painful and happy?

31:26.560 --> 31:28.280
- Yes.
- It sounds complicated.

31:28.360 --> 31:29.680
Do you remember

31:29.760 --> 31:31.200
when we stayed up late every night?

31:31.280 --> 31:33.120
- Seriously.
- We could only eat instant noodles.

31:33.200 --> 31:34.840
Those were hard times.

31:34.920 --> 31:35.920
But it will all pay off.

31:36.680 --> 31:38.320
I'll be returning to my hometown tomorrow.

31:38.400 --> 31:39.520
Are you leaving tomorrow?

31:40.960 --> 31:43.680
- What about you two?
- I'll probably leave tomorrow too.

31:43.760 --> 31:45.680
I wonder if we'll see each other again.

31:46.360 --> 31:47.240
It's okay.

31:47.320 --> 31:48.760
We will get a chance to meet again.

31:50.040 --> 31:50.960
I'm heading inside.

31:51.040 --> 31:52.320
- Okay.
- Okay, I'll see you later.

32:00.880 --> 32:01.720
Jiaxu.

32:04.360 --> 32:06.320
Does that mean it'll be difficult

32:06.400 --> 32:09.680
to see your classmates after graduation?

32:09.760 --> 32:10.800
Two, one.

32:10.880 --> 32:12.040
I guess so.

32:12.960 --> 32:14.200
How do I explain this to you?

32:15.200 --> 32:17.440
We majored in the same discipline,

32:17.960 --> 32:19.360
but after we enter society,

32:19.880 --> 32:22.080
everyone will make their own choice.

32:23.360 --> 32:25.800
Gradually, we'll take different paths.

32:26.560 --> 32:27.520
It could be

32:28.880 --> 32:30.800
that it will be really hard to meet again.

32:39.800 --> 32:42.000
Then what about me?

32:42.560 --> 32:43.440
You?

32:45.880 --> 32:48.280
You're not the same as them.

32:50.280 --> 32:52.720
They won't be like my dear sister

32:53.360 --> 32:54.880
who snuck me a red packet

32:54.960 --> 32:56.440
during Lunar New Year

32:59.760 --> 33:01.000
and even came to give me flowers

33:01.880 --> 33:03.080
on my graduation day.

33:09.480 --> 33:10.680
Don't worry.

33:11.480 --> 33:12.440
After I leave,

33:12.520 --> 33:14.240
I'll come back to see you
whenever I'm free.

33:15.760 --> 33:18.320
When will you be free?

33:20.200 --> 33:22.080
I'll let you know in advance

33:22.160 --> 33:23.000
before I come back.

33:23.720 --> 33:24.640
Okay?

33:32.720 --> 33:34.680
Xiaozhou, can you do me a favor?

33:34.760 --> 33:35.960
Sure.

33:38.440 --> 33:40.200
Help me take a photo with my sister.

33:40.280 --> 33:41.400
Okay.

33:43.360 --> 33:44.320
Hold this.

33:46.080 --> 33:46.960
Come on.

33:47.480 --> 33:48.840
Both of you look at the camera.

33:52.000 --> 33:53.840
Okay, smile a bit more.

34:09.080 --> 34:11.920
- Happy graduation!
- Happy graduation!

34:16.239 --> 34:17.639
Enough. Don't drink too much.

34:18.600 --> 34:19.760
You can't hold your alcohol,

34:19.840 --> 34:21.199
so don't drink too much.

34:21.280 --> 34:22.800
We're celebrating today.

34:23.560 --> 34:24.880
You two are inseparable again.

34:24.960 --> 34:26.840
I have to get to the bottom of this today.

34:26.920 --> 34:28.320
You two always stick together

34:28.400 --> 34:29.600
and never find a girlfriend.

34:30.600 --> 34:31.960
I understand if it's Sang Yan.

34:32.040 --> 34:33.199
With his temper,

34:33.280 --> 34:34.440
who would like him?

34:35.000 --> 34:36.480
Shut up.

34:36.560 --> 34:37.719
Jiaxu, what about you?

34:37.800 --> 34:39.360
Yes. Why don't you have a girlfriend?

34:41.040 --> 34:41.920
What do we say?

34:45.360 --> 34:46.239
See?

34:46.800 --> 34:48.159
That's why we're best buds.

34:48.239 --> 34:49.360
What? Is there a problem?

34:55.880 --> 34:57.240
Duan Jiaxu!

34:57.880 --> 35:00.000
I thought I was your best friend!

35:00.960 --> 35:02.880
How could you have a change of heart?

35:02.960 --> 35:04.720
You are. Of course you are.

35:04.800 --> 35:06.360
Let him be. He's such a crybaby.

35:06.440 --> 35:08.160
- He's ignoring me.
- It's okay.

35:08.240 --> 35:09.480
I'll take care of you. Come.

35:09.560 --> 35:10.520
Are you really crying?

35:10.600 --> 35:12.000
How can you cry for real?

35:12.080 --> 35:13.080
You're a grown-up!

35:14.080 --> 35:15.360
Can someone open a bottle for me?

35:15.440 --> 35:16.600
Give it to me.

35:16.680 --> 35:17.600
Thank you.

35:18.920 --> 35:20.480
Jiaxu, come and have a drink.

35:20.560 --> 35:21.640
- Cheers!
- Cheers, guys.

35:21.720 --> 35:22.640
Happy graduation.

35:22.720 --> 35:24.640
We've graduated, and you're drinking cola?

35:24.720 --> 35:26.160
- Drink beer.
- I can't drink alcohol.

35:26.240 --> 35:27.120
No way.

35:27.200 --> 35:28.880
You're spoiling the fun. Come on.

35:28.960 --> 35:30.000
Give it to me.

35:30.080 --> 35:31.040
Okay, cheers!

35:31.120 --> 35:32.040
Come on, guys.

35:32.120 --> 35:32.960
There they go again.

35:33.040 --> 35:34.320
Are you drinking on his behalf?

35:34.920 --> 35:36.440
Stop wasting time and drink up.

35:36.520 --> 35:37.360
- Drink up!
- Cheers!

35:37.440 --> 35:39.600
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

35:39.680 --> 35:40.640
Jiaxu, drink up.

35:57.720 --> 35:59.200
Don't stop drinking. Finish it.

35:59.280 --> 36:00.720
Is it for the whales or the sharks?

36:00.800 --> 36:02.520
I can finish it. I'll drink first.

36:02.600 --> 36:04.120
Listen. Wait a moment.

36:04.200 --> 36:05.280
I want to ask you something.

36:05.360 --> 36:06.880
- I'll ask you first.
- No, I'll ask you.

36:06.960 --> 36:08.760
- Do you have a crush on her?
- Me?

36:09.480 --> 36:11.000
Do you have a crush on her?

36:11.080 --> 36:12.120
Do you?

36:12.200 --> 36:13.400
Let me finish this drink first.

36:13.880 --> 36:15.720
Today is the last day.

36:15.800 --> 36:16.880
It's the last day, right?

36:16.960 --> 36:17.880
It's the last day.

36:17.960 --> 36:20.280
If you don't tell the truth,
you won't get another chance.

36:20.360 --> 36:21.240
JIANG YING

36:21.320 --> 36:23.200
I'm happy you're coming back to Yihe.

36:23.280 --> 36:24.440
Happy graduation.

36:24.520 --> 36:26.440
CALL CANCELED

36:26.520 --> 36:28.920
I'M HAPPY YOU'RE COMING BACK TO YIHE.
HAPPY GRADUATION.

36:33.720 --> 36:34.960
- What's wrong?
- Jiaxu.

36:35.440 --> 36:36.600
I can't bear to part with you.

36:38.880 --> 36:39.920
Are you drunk?

36:40.000 --> 36:40.840
No.

36:41.800 --> 36:42.680
Why are you alone?

36:42.760 --> 36:43.680
He's drunk.

36:44.400 --> 36:45.600
I'm not.

36:45.680 --> 36:47.080
You are. Stop denying it.

36:47.160 --> 36:48.520
Come. Let's drink.

36:48.600 --> 36:50.920
- Who turned Qian Fei into this?
- Come on, drink.

36:51.400 --> 36:53.200
Come and drink. Qian Fei, here.

36:53.280 --> 36:55.160
- Don't drink with him.
- This is our last time.

37:02.880 --> 37:04.640
- Here.
- Happy graduation, guys!

37:04.720 --> 37:06.280
- Cheers.
- Drink up.

37:32.160 --> 37:33.520
You drank too much.

37:34.960 --> 37:36.800
Jiaxu, I want to ask you something.

37:37.280 --> 37:38.760
When I'm no longer around,

37:38.840 --> 37:39.840
who will watch over you?

37:41.280 --> 37:42.440
Don't worry.

37:42.520 --> 37:44.360
Many people are eyeing me.

37:48.760 --> 37:50.240
Duan Jiaxu.

37:50.760 --> 37:52.600
You and Chen Junwen are going back home.

37:53.200 --> 37:55.320
Only Sang Yan and I will be in Nanwu.

37:56.200 --> 37:57.880
I don't know what is good about Yihe.

37:57.960 --> 37:59.000
Why do you have to go back?

38:00.280 --> 38:01.560
Enough. Let's keep drinking.

38:02.480 --> 38:04.040
You were so loud earlier.

38:04.120 --> 38:05.200
Look at you now.

38:06.000 --> 38:06.880
You're right.

38:13.360 --> 38:14.360
You're home.

38:15.680 --> 38:16.600
Jiaxu.

38:18.360 --> 38:20.080
Will you be okay in Yihe?

38:22.360 --> 38:24.360
Promise me you'll live well in Yihe.

38:24.880 --> 38:26.400
Of course, I'll be fine.

38:28.720 --> 38:29.560
Sit.

38:30.440 --> 38:31.360
Jiaxu.

38:32.360 --> 38:34.520
You must come and visit us regularly.

38:36.880 --> 38:38.200
I'll come back often.

38:40.280 --> 38:41.160
Sang Yan.

38:42.000 --> 38:43.280
Are you home?

38:43.360 --> 38:45.280
- Mr. and Mrs. Sang.
- Xiaoduan, you're here too.

38:45.360 --> 38:47.080
What's wrong? Did he drink too much?

38:47.160 --> 38:48.600
We celebrated our graduation.

38:49.440 --> 38:52.120
- Why did he drink so much?
- Thank you for bringing him home.

38:52.200 --> 38:53.040
Give him some water.

38:53.120 --> 38:54.800
- Okay.
- I'll make hangover soup for him.

38:54.880 --> 38:55.720
Okay.

38:55.800 --> 38:57.600
Why did he push himself to drink so much?

38:57.680 --> 38:59.320
Sang Yan, have some water.

39:01.120 --> 39:02.880
- Move slowly.
- I'm going to go, Mrs. Sang.

39:02.960 --> 39:05.280
Wait. Where are you spending the night?

39:05.360 --> 39:07.680
There's an inn nearby.

39:07.760 --> 39:10.640
Don't waste money.
Just sleep in Sang Yan's room.

39:10.720 --> 39:11.760
Don't go to the trouble.

39:11.840 --> 39:13.120
Not at all.

39:13.200 --> 39:14.520
Zhizhi, you're here too.

39:14.600 --> 39:15.800
Xiaoduan will spend the night.

39:15.880 --> 39:17.760
Get him a new towel and toothbrush.

39:17.840 --> 39:19.720
It's really okay, Mrs. Sang. I can manage.

39:20.280 --> 39:22.720
Stop turning me down. Go upstairs now.

39:23.480 --> 39:24.360
It's all right.

39:26.040 --> 39:27.080
Are you feeling better now?

39:27.160 --> 39:28.920
- Thank you for having me.
- It's no problem.

39:30.840 --> 39:31.880
Bring him upstairs.

39:32.520 --> 39:33.840
